have h2 : ∀ ω, IsCadlag (X · ω) := hX.cadlag
have h3 : ⨆ i, eLpNorm (X i) 2 P < ∞ := hX.bounded
```

These are the properties of a square integrable martingale. Now we need to prove the monotonicity of the `eLpNorm`.

```tactics
