So `E[‖X j‖ ^ 2 | F i] ≥ ‖X i‖ ^ 2`. 

Now, to prove `∫ Ω ‖X i ω‖ ^ 2 dP ω ≤ ∫ Ω ‖X j ω‖ ^ 2 dP ω`, we can use the fact that `‖X j‖ ^ 2` is a submartingale. 

